query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.status, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM assets a WHERE a.projectId = p.id) as asset_count
FROM projects p 
WHERE p.name LIKE '%Edmonton%' OR p.name LIKE '%City of Edmonton%'
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
